<div class="com-share" data-id="24137" data-title="《奢侈品在中国继续关店，但COACH打算多开店》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/24137/medium/24137.jpg?1458317273" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/24137.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
